## ðŸ§° Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **React.js** â€“ Interactive UI with component-based architecture
- **Three.js / react-three-fiber** â€“ Integration of 3D models into the frontend
- **Chart.js / Recharts** â€“ Displaying score analytics in dashboard
- **Axios** â€“ API communication

### Backend
- **Node.js + Express.js** â€“ RESTful APIs and server logic
- **MongoDB + Mongoose** â€“ Storing user data, scores, bookmarks, content, etc.

### Others
- **Blender** â€“ 3D model creation and animation
- **Chatbot** â€“ Integrated using third-party APIs 
- **JWT Auth** â€“ User authentication and protected routes

